### 列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts

### 列表（按分类）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts?categorySlug=java

### 详情（与前端文章 id 一致）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts/java-spring-boot-blog-api

### 新建（VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP Client 可点 Run）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "REST 测试",
  "subtitle": "副标题",
  "category": "Java 后端",
  "categorySlug": "java",
  "tags": ["REST"],
  "date": "2026-03-25",
  "readTime": 1,
  "pinned": false,
  "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "text": "正文" }]
}

### Echo（练习 POST）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/learn/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "张三", "note": "hello" }
